channel.title: PROJECT DARK EVOLUTION V1 [500+ Views]
channel.description:
NOT LEECHED
This topic is mainly about me saying sorry to people and giving you a little something in return for thanks.
My Speech: I am very sorry moparscapers, will you forgive me after i will apoligise 1 million times if it takes for anyone to forgive me, will you forgive me after i give you this? i have been wrong at times but so have you.. So please will you just forgive me!?
Why did i release this client? Thanksgiving and a sorry speech to everyone, also this.. Because it is a client with most of silabsoft items and has custom items added. This client contains Dragon Claws, Dragon Full Helm, Dragon Platebody, Dragon Pickaxe and many many more.. It is able to change the connecting IP and Port!
Features:
* Added Changable Connecting IP and Port * Added Most of the Silabsoft Models * Added Most of the Custom Items * Added Brand New Interface (Design) * Added New Dlight Codex
Containing Added Models/Items
* DClaws * DFull Helm * DPickaxe * DPlatebody * Bandos Helm * Bandos Scimitar * Dark Cape
Pictures:
[IMG]http://i725.photobucket.com/albums/ww255/dcrew09/darkevo1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i725.photobucket.com/albums/ww255/dcrew09/darkevo2.jpg[/img]
Credits:
60% Me 30% Skittlez 10% Moparscape
Information:
Skittlez only provided the base I Provided All Above Features Moparscape Provided Help and Support People Provided Mivering for a 317 IP Changing Client
Download:
Mediafire: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?2hznjmdhzfz]http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?2hznjmdhzfz[/url]
Please report any errors/bugs to me, If any support is needed, Come to me.. I will provide anything for anyone in return of thanks and support, I really would like to thanks all of Moparscape team and all Moparscapers for every last drop of support, thank you all so very much, please dont flame and thanks again.
CLOSED SOURCE - Due to people leeching and flaming me and not giving me credits.
I may think otherwise for an open source if i get respect, credits, nice and friendly comments.
Moparscape does not put up for abuse, flame, leeching and neither do I.
Treat me with respect and i will treat you with respect, Thank you very much for your time.
And to people who hate me or hold anything against me, I am sorry please forgive me.
In return here is my sorry video and celebration to forget all sins for all moparscapers
[url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=305vRNoofr8]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=305vRNoofr8[/url]
Please goto the above forgiveness video.
